<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#ActivityOccurrence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "One performed activity within a VisitOccurrence. Uses the universal substrate pattern: any assessment (vitals, MRI, ePRO, biopsy, IP administration) uses the same entity shape; content specialisation is via biomedicalConceptCode and taskValueType. FHIR R5: Procedure / Observation / MedicationAdministration (per activity type). SDTM: domain depends on type (VS, LB, EG, EX, PE, etc.)." .
