<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#ActivityTemplate> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The protocol-defined activity template: the procedure to perform at a visit. USDM-ingest-derivable from StudyDesign.activities[]. Carries the biomedical-concept code that determines what kind of data the activity collects. USDM: Activity." .
