<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#OperationalRecord> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Non-clinical, non-GCP-governed data captured during trial operations — process metrics, site performance indicators, sponsor-defined operational fields (e.g. X_WHATEVER extensions in Medidata). Not an hcls:Observation (no clinical value) and not directly regulated by ICH E6; captured in operational CRFs or sponsor-specific payloads. Primary target for LLM-assisted field-mapping inference (cr:mappingConfidence)." .
