<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SeriousAdverseEvent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Serious Adverse Event" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SeriousAdverseEvent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#AdverseEvent> .
