<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#ServiceProvider> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A party to whom a sponsor or investigator transfers specified trial-related duties and functions (paraphrased, ICH E6(R3)). The CRO is a specialized service provider." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#ShipSample> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Action> .
