<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteActivation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteActivation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The green-light record (observedAt = activated date); must cite IRB approval, executed CTA, and SIV." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteActivation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Site Activation" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteActivation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Temporal> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteActivation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Versioned> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteBoundary> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteBoundary> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Site" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteCoordinator> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteCoordinator> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The day-to-day clinical operations professional at a Site. Screens and enrolls participants, executes visits, completes CRFs, manages AE reporting, and maintains site logs. Also known as Clinical Research Coordinator (CRC). OOUX persona aliases: Coordinator, Study Coordinator, CRC." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteCoordinator> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Site Coordinator" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteCoordinator> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Practitioner> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteInitiationVisit> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteInitiationVisit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The visit that prepares and activates a site for enrollment." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteInitiationVisit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Site Initiation Visit (SIV)" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteInitiationVisit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Temporal> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteInitiationVisit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Versioned> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteSelectionDecision> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteSelectionDecision> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A recorded, provenance-tagged decision about a study site at a specific lifecycle transition. Captures both positive (Selected, Reserve) and negative (Dropped) outcomes with mandatory rationale. The negative path — why a site was not selected — is institutional intelligence that is almost never captured in practice today but is essential for: (a) sponsor learning across studies, (b) avoiding repeat qualification of unsuitable sites, (c) CRO accountability. Bitemporal (top:Versioned) because decisions can be revised (a Dropped site can become Reserve under rescue conditions)." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteSelectionDecision> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Site Selection Decision" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteSelectionDecision> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Evidence> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteSelectionDecision> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Versioned> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteSelectionSubPhase> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Phase> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteSelectionSubPhase> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Feasibility assessment, site evaluation, qualification visit (SQV), site selection committee review. Output: selected site list with signed contracts." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteSelectionSubPhase> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Site Selection" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteStatusActive> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteStatusActive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Site is actively enrolling or conducting the trial (post-SIV, first subject possible or enrolled)." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteStatusActive> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Active" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteStatusClosed> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteStatusClosed> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Site close-out visit completed; no further subject activity; eTMF finalization in progress." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteStatusClosed> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Closed" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteStatusDropped> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteStatusDropped> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Site was not selected or was withdrawn after selection. The reason MUST be captured in a cr:SiteSelectionDecision — this is institutional intelligence almost never recorded today." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteStatusDropped> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Dropped" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteStatusFeasibility> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteStatusFeasibility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Site is under feasibility assessment: SQV scheduled or completed, selection committee review pending." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteStatusFeasibility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Feasibility" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteStatusReserve> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteStatusReserve> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Site has passed feasibility but is held in reserve as a rescue site. Sponsor may activate it if enrollment falls short at active sites. Distinct from Selected: no startup work has begun." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteStatusReserve> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Reserve" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteStatusSelected> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteStatusSelected> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Site has been selected: contracts signed, Study Startup Package in preparation." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteStatusSelected> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Selected" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteStatusStartup> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteStatusStartup> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Site Initiation Visit completed or in progress; staff training, delegation of authority, equipment qualification underway." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteStatusStartup> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Startup" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SourceData> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SourceData> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.ich.org/page/efficacy-guidelines> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SourceData> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Source Data" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SourceData> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Evidence> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SourceData> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Versioned> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SourceData> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The original recorded information, and certified copies of it, needed to reconstruct and evaluate the trial (paraphrased, ICH E6(R3))." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SourceDocument> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SourceDocument> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <https://www.ich.org/page/efficacy-guidelines> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SourceDocument> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Source Document" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SourceDocument> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#EssentialRecord> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SourceDocument> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The original document/record holding source data (paraphrased, ICH E6(R3))." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#Sponsor> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#Sponsor> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The organization that initiates and is accountable for the trial." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#Sponsor> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Sponsor" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#Sponsor> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Organization> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SponsorBoundary> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#NamedIndividual> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SponsorBoundary> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Sponsor" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SponsorOperationsStaff> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SponsorOperationsStaff> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Manages protocol amendments, site network structure, regions, country configuration, site activation mechanics, and system configuration. OOUX persona aliases: Sponsor Operations, Sponsor Ops, Site Activation Manager." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SponsorOperationsStaff> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Sponsor Operations" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SponsorOperationsStaff> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Person> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SponsorProjectManager> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SponsorProjectManager> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Creates and activates studies, selects and manages sites, tracks milestones and enrollment, and closes studies. OOUX persona aliases: Sponsor PM, Study PM, Project Manager, Study Manager." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SponsorProjectManager> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Sponsor Project Manager" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SponsorProjectManager> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Person> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SponsorQualityStaff> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SponsorQualityStaff> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Classifies, approves, and closes deviations. Conducts audits and risk assessments; manages CAPAs. OOUX persona aliases: Sponsor Quality, Quality, Auditor." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SponsorQualityStaff> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Sponsor Quality" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SponsorQualityStaff> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Person> .
