<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#StartVisit> <https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#operatesOn> <https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#VisitOccurrence> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#StartupArtifact> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#StartupArtifact> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A document instance in (or produced from) the start-up package, classified to a TMF artifact type. Carries the data that the work streams consume and transform." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#StartupArtifact> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Start-up Artifact" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#StartupArtifact> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Evidence> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#StartupPhase> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Phase> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#StartupPhase> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Everything from initial protocol design through first-patient-in (FPI). Gate condition: first participant randomized. Canonical ICH E6(R3) pre-trial period." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#StartupPhase> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Startup" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#StartupPhase> <https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#contains> <https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#ActivationSubPhase> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#StartupPhase> <https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#contains> <https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#DesignSubPhase> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#StartupPhase> <https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#contains> <https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#RegulatorySubPhase> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#StartupPhase> <https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#contains> <https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#SiteSelectionSubPhase> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#StartupPhase> <https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#precedes> <https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#ConductPhase> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#StatisticalAnalysisPlan> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#StatisticalAnalysisPlan> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The pre-specified plan for analyzing the study's data." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#StatisticalAnalysisPlan> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Statistical Analysis Plan" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#StatisticalAnalysisPlan> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Evidence> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#StoppingRule> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#StoppingRule> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A safety rule that halts dosing or enrollment when triggered." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#StoppingRule> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Stopping Rule" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#StoppingRule> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Constraint> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#Study> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#Study> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A clinical study — the unit of investigation the protocol defines." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#Study> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Study" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#Study> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Scope> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#StudyEvent> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#StudyEvent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A scheduled or unscheduled timepoint (StudyEventOID) when data is captured." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#StudyEvent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Study Event" .
