<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#Visit> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#Visit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A protocol visit — a kind of study event." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#Visit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Trial Visit" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#Visit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#StudyEvent> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#Visit> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Temporal> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#VisitDefinition> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#VisitDefinition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The protocol-defined visit template: what is SUPPOSED to happen (type, window, mode, ordering). USDM-ingest-derivable from StudyDesign.encounters[]. UNSCHEDULED visits (urgent care, AE workup) have no VisitDefinition; their VisitOccurrence.definedBy is absent. USDM: Encounter. SDTM projection: SE (Study Elements) domain." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#VisitDefinition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Visit Definition" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#VisitDefinition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#VisitDefinition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Scope> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#VisitExecutionSubPhase> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Phase> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#VisitExecutionSubPhase> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Scheduled and unscheduled visit conduct: actuals vs. SOA, activity completion, IP administration, sample collection, CRF completion at visit level." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#VisitExecutionSubPhase> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Visit Execution" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#VisitOccurrence> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#VisitOccurrence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An actual protocol visit: what DID happen. Anchored at Participant (1..1) and StudySite (1..1). Optionally definedBy a VisitDefinition (absent for unscheduled visits). FHIR R5: Encounter. SDTM: SV domain (SVSTDTC / SVENDTC / VISITNUM / VISIT). OMOP: VISIT_OCCURRENCE." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#VisitOccurrence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Visit Occurrence" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#VisitOccurrence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Activity> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#VisitOccurrence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Temporal> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#VisitOccurrence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Versioned> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#Window> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#Window> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An allowed tolerance around a planned time: a lower and an upper offset in days (e.g. [-2 days, +2 days])." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#Window> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Window" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1#Window> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Constraint> .
