<https://top.scientix.ai/cr/v1> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/rights> "Includes an independent derivative adaptation of the ICH E6(R3) Good Clinical Practice Guideline (Step 4, 2025; Principles, Glossary, Annex 1) — paraphrased, not endorsed or sponsored by ICH, original copyright © ICH. TMF artifact types align by name to the DIA TMF Reference Model (licensed; no text reproduced). See the repository NOTICE file." .
