<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "OWNED, provenance-tagged crosswalks from TOP/CR-core to external ontologies. Aligns to SSSOM slots (subject_id/predicate_id/object_id/mapping_justification/confidence/author_id/mapping_date); an SSSOM TSV is an edge projection of these. Crosswalks are assertions WE own and curate, never imports of the external ontology." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "TOP crosswalk vocabulary (SSSOM-aligned)" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#Mapping> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#Mapping> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A curated, provenanced correspondence from a TOP term to an external ontology term." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#Mapping> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Crosswalk Mapping" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#Mapping> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Evidence> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#author> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#author> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The curator/agent IRI (SSSOM author_id)." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#author> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "author id" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#confidence> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#confidence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "confidence" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#confidence> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#decimal> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#confirmedAt> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#confirmedAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Timestamp when a mapping was confirmed by a human reviewer. Together with cx:confirmedBy, closes the audit trail for human-in-the-loop validation." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#confirmedAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "confirmed at" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#confirmedAt> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#confirmedBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#confirmedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The human agent (or committee) that reviewed and confirmed a proposed mapping. Required for promotion from 'under_review' to 'confirmed'." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#confirmedBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "confirmed by" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#inferredBy> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#inferredBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The top:AutonomousAgent instance that proposed this mapping via LLM inference. Enables provenance tracing back to the agent model and prompt version." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#inferredBy> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "inferred by" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#justification> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#justification> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A semapv justification IRI (e.g. ManualMappingCuration)." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#justification> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "mapping justification" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#mappingDate> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#mappingDate> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "mapping date" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#mappingDate> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#mappingMethod> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#mappingMethod> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "How the mapping was produced: ManualCuration | LLMInference | RuleBasedExtraction | HybridReview. Drives downstream trust and routing." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#mappingMethod> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "mapping method" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#mappingRationale> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#mappingRationale> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Human-readable explanation of why this mapping was proposed, especially for LLM-inferred mappings. Mirrors top:rationale on a Conclusion." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#mappingRationale> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "mapping rationale" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#mappingRationale> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#objectId> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#objectId> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The external ontology term (right side)." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#objectId> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "object id" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#predicateId> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#predicateId> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "SKOS mapping predicate." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#predicateId> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "predicate id" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#retrievedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#retrievedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The primary source the target IRI was verified against (URL + retrieval date)." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#retrievedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "retrieved from" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#reviewStatus> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#reviewStatus> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Lifecycle state of the mapping: proposed | under_review | confirmed | rejected | deprecated. Confirmed mappings graduate from ephemeral inference to Layer-2 crosswalk." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#reviewStatus> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "review status" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#subjectId> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#subjectId> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The TOP/CR-core term (left side)." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#subjectId> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "subject id" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#verificationStatus> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#verificationStatus> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "verified | unverified | deprecated — whether the target IRI was confirmed against a primary source." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/crosswalk/v1#verificationStatus> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "verification status" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Mid-layer specializing TOP Core for entities that recur across >=2 HCLS domains (clinical research, hospital, manufacturing, pharmacovigilance, RWE, commercialization). Seeded minimally; grows by promotion (rule of three). Standards projection target: FHIR, OMOP." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "HCLS-core" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Action> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Action> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A named, authorized operation (Call To Action in OOUX terms) that an agent of a given type may perform in a given Phase. Actions are reference-graph archetypes (top:Constraint: they specify what is authorized). Realized occurrences in instance graphs are prov:Activity individuals linked back via hcls:realizationOf." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Action> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Action" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Action> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Constraint> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Clinician> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Clinician> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A licensed clinician who provides or oversees clinical care or research. Specializes in sub-domains: Investigator (clinical research), Physician (clinical care), Pharmacist, etc." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Clinician> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Clinician" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Clinician> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Practitioner> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Condition> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Condition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A diagnosed state of a Person." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Condition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Condition" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Condition> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Outcome> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Consent> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Consent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An act of agreement by a Person authorizing an action or use of their data/person. HCLS-universal: permutates to cr:InformedConsentAct (clinical trial enrollment), HIPAA Authorization (data use), Treatment Consent (clinical care). Carries valid-time (when consent was given, when it expires) and transaction-time (when it was recorded)." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Consent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Consent" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Consent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Temporal> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Consent> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Versioned> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#HealthcareFacility> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#HealthcareFacility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A physical place where care or research is conducted." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#HealthcareFacility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Healthcare Facility" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#HealthcareFacility> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Location> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#JobToBeDone> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#JobToBeDone> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A bounded unit of operator intent: the goal an agent type is trying to achieve, with a trigger condition and measurable success signals. Scoped to an agent type (OWL class) and a Phase. References the object graph and authorized Actions involved. Derived from OOUX JTBD blocks." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#JobToBeDone> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Job to Be Done" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#JobToBeDone> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Scope> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Lot> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Lot> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A manufactured batch/lot; the primary join to the manufacturing domain." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Lot> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Lot" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Lot> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Resource> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#MedicinalProduct> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#MedicinalProduct> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A medicinal product (drug or biologic)." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#MedicinalProduct> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Medicinal Product" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#MedicinalProduct> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Resource> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Observation> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Observation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An information artifact recording a measured value; refersTo the Person/Specimen it is about." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Observation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Observation" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Observation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Evidence> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Organization> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Organization> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "An organization — sponsor, CRO, site, central lab, or regulator." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Organization> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Organization" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Organization> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Agent> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Person> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Person> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A human. BOUNDARY-ONLY / PII layer: an identifiable Person lives inside the source/site sovereign boundary. Downstream and shareable artifacts must attach to a pseudonymous cr:StudySubject, never to a Person. The only legal Person<->Subject link is the attested Enrollment bridge (cr:enrolledPerson). Clinical data is PSEUDONYMIZED, not anonymized: re-identification is preserved but controlled (safety / emergency unblinding)." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Person> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Person" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Person> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Agent> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Phase> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Phase> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A bounded, sequenced stage of a process lifecycle within an HCLS domain. Phases form a containment tree (hcls:contains) and a precedence chain (hcls:precedes). Permutates to: cr:StartupPhase/ConductPhase/CloseoutPhase (clinical research); Admission/Inpatient/Discharge (clinical care); Formulation/Fill-Finish/Release (manufacturing)." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Phase> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Phase" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Phase> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Scope> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Practitioner> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Practitioner> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A healthcare professional." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Practitioner> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Practitioner" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Practitioner> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Person> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Specimen> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Specimen> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A biospecimen collected from a Person." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Specimen> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Specimen" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Specimen> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Resource> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Substance> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Substance> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A chemical or biological substance." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Substance> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Substance" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Substance> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf> <https://top.scientix.ai/v1#Resource> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#actsAs> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#actsAs> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "At instance-graph time, a human-readable label for the contextual role a Person plays within a Scope (Study, Site, Care Episode). Not a class; purely a string annotation on the Person-Scope binding. Example value: 'Principal Investigator'." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#actsAs> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Person> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#actsAs> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "acts as" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#affiliatedWith> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#affiliatedWith> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Person> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#affiliatedWith> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "affiliated with" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#affiliatedWith> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Organization> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#authorizedAgentType> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#authorizedAgentType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "The OWL class of agent authorized to execute this Action. Authorization binds directly to agent type — no OperatorRole intermediary. Multi-valued: an Action may be authorized for more than one agent type." .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#authorizedAgentType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Action> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#authorizedAgentType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "authorized agent type" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#authorizedAgentType> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#collectedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#ObjectProperty> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#collectedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain> <https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Specimen> .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#collectedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "collected from" .
<https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#collectedFrom> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#range> <https://top.scientix.ai/hcls/v1#Person> .
